{"tid":1145804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南非大選討論區","createTime":"2019-05-09T00:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T02:23:18.000Z","uid":37197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18419a459772a08a9b8aec8f3c030aff1cb94c07","tid":1145804,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:45:05.000Z","msg":"今年係南非第六屆既大選<br />\n同以往唔同既係，今年選情特別激烈<br />\n主要由ANC (非洲國民議會) DA (民主聯盟) 同埋新興既EFF (經濟自由戰士) 角逐400個議席<br />\n<br />\nANC: 由曼德拉成立，自廢除種族隔離後執政至今，上年取得近64% 選票， 但近年受貪污醜聞、經濟停濟，失業高企， 總統祖馬落台，由拉馬福薩繼任。 <br />\n<br />\nDC: 由南非荷蘭人成立既政黨，今年由黑人領袖 Mmusi Maimane 參選總統，一直係最大既在野黨<br />\nEFF: 由ANC 分裂出黎既政黨，主張反貪污，同埋種族議題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主張沒收白人土地，將白人財產分配黑人等等。吸引唔小支持者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news24.com/Elections/Results/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news24.com%2FElections%2FResults%2F&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=f886b9be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news24.com/Elections/Results/</a>"},{"pid":"2b0dabed40e2fdb6f856032c3f7aba485c941a2d","tid":1145804,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:45:57.000Z","msg":"大家可以留意下， 有時都唔太明 ANC依個管治失敗但仍有大量黑人支持，唔同廢除種族隔離真係上左神枱"},{"pid":"1b7a2d97ac8da52ce936a99073824a783cb78e46","tid":1145804,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:46:25.000Z","msg":"DA 定DC？<br />\n有d睇唔明"},{"pid":"f44de456bd7474aaf532089ad23a87852b0c7c7e","tid":1145804,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b7a2d97ac8da52ce936a99073824a783cb78e46","tid":1145804,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:46:25.000Z","msg":"DA 定DC？<br />\n有d睇唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"DA 先岩唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h